snippet.title: Amber Heard Filmography
snippet.description: My father always encouraged me to be an actress. I guess, as a parent, you can look at your child and see what they are kind of prone to and I was that kid; I had a video camera when I was a child and filmed everything and organized plays and I was always on camera too. I would never just be behind the camera, hello! I would put myself in as the star. I did do the plays in high school before I dropped out and finished high school on my own. I fell in love with theater in high school and it was something that my parents really encouraged, probably up until the moment I said `I`m gonna go do it tomorrow`. They`ve been great. - aheardfan.com

Donald Wells said that Summer and her grandmother and mother were outside planting flowers Tuesday evening. snippet.title: "I'M THE FATHER" Elon Musk REACTS To Rumors On Being Amber Heard's BABY DADDY | The Gossipy
snippet.description:
"I'M THE FATHER" Elon Musk REACTS To Rumors On Being Amber Heard's BABY DADDY | The Gossipy

Elon Musk just keeps getting dragged back into the Johnny Depp Amber Heard celeb drama. Elon Musk, Johnny Depp and Amber Heard are back on the frontlines of celebrity news. Amber Heard just had a baby girl and rumors are swirling on who the baby's father is. Many are saying it is Johnny Depp. Some are saying is Elon Musk himself. Elon Musk and Amber Heard are past lovers and rumors are swirling that Elon Musk paid Amber Heard's 7 million donation to the ACLU back in 2016. So these two have a history together.

But no public statements have been made in this regard by either Elon Musk, Johnny Depp or Amber Heard. So no one knows for sure yet. In this video, we breakdown the story in detail. This celebrity drama goes down while the Johnny Depp Amber Heard civil court case rages on.

With the initial court date being pushed back, Johnny Depp and Amber Heard have been given some more time in order to gather more evidence for their individual cases. For quite some time, the two were firing evidence at each other in order to win in court. 

Ever since the recent release of the footage of the LAPD officers from the penthouse night of Amber Heard and Johnny Depp, things have not been looking all too bright for Amber Heard. Her team has been working tirelessly in order to back up her side, however Johnny Depp seems to have made the attempt to strike back.

snippet.title: The Adderall Diaries Official Trailer #1 (2016) - James Franco, Amber Heard Movie HD
snippet.description:
The Adderall Diaries Official Trailer #1 (2016) - James Franco, Amber Heard Movie HD
Subscribe: https://goo.gl/sgnqiT

As a writer stymied by past success, writers block, substance abuse, relationship problems and a serious set of father issues, Elliott's cracked-out chronicle of a bizarre murder trial amounts to less than the sum of its parts. Not long into the 2007 trial of programmer Hans Reiser, accused of murdering his wife, the defendant's friend Sean Sturgeon obliquely confessed to several murders (though not the murder of Reiser's wife). Elliott, caught up in the film-ready twist and his tenuous connection to Sturgeon (they share a BDSM social circle), makes a gonzo record of the proceedings. The result is a scattered, self-indulgent romp through the mind of a depressive narcissist obsessed with his insecurities and childhood traumas. 

Director: Pamela Romanowsky
Writers: Stephen Elliott (memoir), Pamela Romanowsky (screenplay)
Stars: Amber Heard, James Franco, Christian Slater
